<barrons:question>
<![CDATA[<TextFlow xmlns="http://ns.adobe.com/textLayout/2008">
<p>What is the surface area, in square inches, of a cube whose volume is 216 cubic inches?</p>
</TextFlow>]]>
</barrons:question>

<barrons:choices>
<barrons:choice correct="false"><![CDATA[<TextFlow xmlns="http://ns.adobe.com/textLayout/2008"><p>36</p></TextFlow>]]></barrons:choice>
<barrons:choice correct="false"><![CDATA[<TextFlow xmlns="http://ns.adobe.com/textLayout/2008"><p>54</p></TextFlow>]]></barrons:choice>
<barrons:choice correct="true"><![CDATA[<TextFlow xmlns="http://ns.adobe.com/textLayout/2008"><p>216</p></TextFlow>]]></barrons:choice>
<barrons:choice correct="false"><![CDATA[<TextFlow xmlns="http://ns.adobe.com/textLayout/2008"><p>324</p></TextFlow>]]></barrons:choice>
<barrons:choice correct="false"><![CDATA[<TextFlow xmlns="http://ns.adobe.com/textLayout/2008"><p>1,296</p></TextFlow>]]></barrons:choice>
</barrons:choices>

<barrons:explanation>
<![CDATA[<TextFlow xmlns="http://ns.adobe.com/textLayout/2008">
<p><span fontWeight="bold">216</span></p>
<p>Since the volume of the cube is 216 cubic inches, we have <span fontStyle="italic">e</span><span baselineShift="superscript">3</span> = 216 <img dominantBaseline="ideographicCenter" source="assets/images/double_arrow.swf"/> <span fontStyle="italic">e</span> = 6. The area of each face is <span fontStyle="italic">e</span><span baselineShift="superscript">2</span> = 36 square inches, and since there are six faces, the total surface area is 6 &#215; 36 = 216 square inches.</p>
</TextFlow>]]>
</barrons:explanation>
